## Part 1 – Network Architecture (OSI Layers 1–3)

The WBMUD network was designed using three main operational segments and one DMZ segment. The IT network represents the office environment, the OT network represents industrial control systems, and the Remote Pump Station represents a remote operational site connected through WAN links.

